dc_description_s: This polyline shapefile depicts all hiking, biking and equestrian trails managed by the County of San Mateo, California. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for San Mateo County, California.This coverage can be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analyses of geospatial data.
